## Workflow Explanation
The user currently uses local scripts. The simplest path to GitHub is:
1. Run [create-post.ps1](file:///C:/Users/maiku/.gemini/antigravity/create-post.ps1) (Local)
2. Run [update_blog.bat](file:///C:/Users/maiku/.gemini/antigravity/update_blog.bat) (Local)
3. Commit all changes (HTML + JS) and push.
GitHub Pages will verify the static HTML/JS as is.
